sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Admin
    participant Vault
    participant Custody
    participant Pruv as MockPruv
    participant AMM as MockAMM
    participant USDC as MockUSDC

    Note over Admin: Step 0: update NAV before epoch
    Admin->>Pruv: setPrice(newWRWAPrice)

    Admin->>Vault: processEpoch()
    activate Vault

    Note over Vault: Step 1: Snapshot queues
    Vault->>Vault: subQueueUSDC = sum(pending sub)
    Vault->>Vault: redeemQueueShares = sum(pending redeem)
    Vault->>Pruv: pricePerWRWA()
    Pruv-->>Vault: price
    Vault->>Custody: balances (wRWA, liquid, USDC)
    Custody-->>Vault: balances
    Vault->>Vault: nav = totalAssets / totalSupply

    Note over Vault: Step 2: Matching (P2P)
    Vault->>Vault: matched = min(subUSDC, redeemUSDC)
    Vault->>Vault: distribute matched shares pro-rata to subs
    Vault->>Vault: distribute matched USDC pro-rata to redeemers
    Vault->>Vault: burn matched portion of redeemer shares

    alt subUSDC > redeemUSDC (Sub > Redeem case)
        Note over Vault: Step 3a: Settle net sub (buy assets)
        Vault->>Vault: netSub = subUSDC - redeemUSDC
        Vault->>Vault: compute target buy split (rebalance toward 80/20)
        Vault->>Custody: depositUSDC(buyIlliquid + buyLiquid)
        Vault->>Custody: subscribeToPruv(buyIlliquid)
        Custody->>USDC: approve + transfer to Pruv
        Custody->>Pruv: subscribe(buyIlliquid)
        Pruv-->>Custody: wRWA minted
        Vault->>Custody: swapUSDCForLiquid(buyLiquid)
        Custody->>USDC: approve + transfer to AMM
        Custody->>AMM: swap(USDC → liquid)
        AMM-->>Custody: liquid tokens
        Vault->>Vault: mint additional shares to net sub subscribers
    else redeemUSDC > subUSDC (Redeem > Sub case)
        Note over Vault: Step 3b: Settle net redeem (3-layer)
        Vault->>Vault: netRedeem = redeemUSDC - subUSDC

        Note over Vault,Custody: Layer 2 — Liquid buffer
        Vault->>Custody: liquidBalance()
        Custody-->>Vault: liquidAvail
        Vault->>Custody: swapLiquidForUSDC(min(need, liquidAvail))
        Custody->>AMM: swap(liquid → USDC)
        AMM-->>Custody: USDC

        Note over Vault,Custody: Layer 3 — Illiquid (if needed)
        opt liquid insufficient
            Vault->>Custody: redeemFromPruv(remaining/price)
            Custody->>Pruv: redeem(wRWAAmount)
            Pruv-->>Custody: USDC returned
        end

        Vault->>Custody: withdrawUSDC(redeemers, payouts)
        Custody->>USDC: transfer to each redeemer
        Vault->>Vault: burn shares of net redeem requesters
    else exact match
        Note over Vault: Step 3c: No asset action needed
    end

    Note over Vault: Step 4: Mark queues processed
    Vault->>Vault: emit EpochProcessed(epoch, ...)
    deactivate Vault

    Note over Admin,USDC: Users can now claim() against processed requests
